</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idf6ac931f-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idf6ac9320-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1989-01-01">Jan. 1, 1989</date>, with certain exceptions and qualifications, see <ref href="/us/pl/100/710/s107">section 107 of Pub. L. 100–710</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t46/s31301">section 31301 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
